# Licensing Structure

This project uses multiple licenses for different components:

## User-Facing Applications (GPL v3)
The following modules are licensed under the GNU General Public License v3:
- **viewer/** - Interactive 3D floorplan viewer application
- **mcp-server/** - Model Context Protocol server for Claude integration

Copyright (C) 2025-2026 Malar Kannan

See the LICENSE file in each directory for the full GPL v3 license text.

## Core Libraries (MIT License)
The following libraries are licensed under the MIT License:
- **floorplan-3d-core/** - Shared 3D rendering primitives
- **floorplan-common/** - Shared utilities and geometry functions

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 Malar Kannan

## Language Grammar (MIT License - Dual Copyright)
- **language/** - Langium-based DSL parser and validator

Copyright (c) 2025 Alexander Lang
Copyright (c) 2025-2026 Malar Kannan

